      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for sustained performance and roadworthiness. Featuring a documented service history and a well-preserved interior, this vehicle offers a refined driving experience for the discerning professional. We invite you to inspect this exceptional offering and appreciate its superior caliber firsthand.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s looking for a new adventure! This car has been so good to me\u2014it\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a champ. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today. You\u2019re going to love how it handles! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2004 E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 straight-six power plant with its signature individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp tactile engagement, paired with the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. A driver-focused example in solid mechanical health, showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, but mechanically sorted for the spirited driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Well-maintained.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish that still holds a showroom shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front hood consistent with highway driving. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features, including the high-fidelity sound system and navigation, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals with high-quality synthetic oil, and the transmission provides smooth, predictable shifts. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been parked in a climate-controlled garage, ensuring it remains in great shape for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a superior blend of performance and sophisticated engineering. This unit has been subjected to a comprehensive professional evaluation to ensure structural integrity and optimal operational efficiency. With its refined aesthetic and dependable mechanical profile, it represents a premier acquisition for the discerning motorist who prioritizes both value and excellence in their next automotive investment. We invite you to inspect this exceptional example of craftsmanship.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants something dependable and ready to hit the road. It's been well-loved and taken care of, so it runs like a dream. I've honestly enjoyed every mile in it, and I\u2019m sure you will too! Drop me a message if you\u2019re interested\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential analog performance machine. At its heart is the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system that has been recently serviced for optimal cam timing. This example features a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate chassis fatigue and upgraded rod bearings for long-term peace of mind. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile engagement and predictable power delivery. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative steering and neutral handling balance characteristic of the M-division's peak era. While showing light patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain is robust, and the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. A superb choice for the enthusiast seeking a sorted, high-revving driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
